Au7-lai5 i tu2-tioh8 chin choe7 e5 gui5-hiam2 chong2-si7 long2 sin3-kho3 Siong7-te3 lai5 tek-seng3. I kong2, ¡§Siat-su2 Mou5-kui2 chhin-chhiunn7 chhu3-hia7 hiah-nih choe7, goa2 ia7 bo5 kiann i.¡¨
