Hut-jian5 Jit8-pun2 sip8-kek Chin-chu-oan e5 siau-sit kau3. Chin-chiann3 si7 chit8 e5 chin thang kiann e5 cha2-khi2. Hut-jian5 Jit8-pun2 hian3-peng chhoa7 che7-che7 kun-peng lai5, chiong sou2 u7 e5 Bi2-kok, Eng-kok e5 soan-kau3-su long2 eng7 chhiu2-khau3 ka7 in khau3 tiau5 leh. Chiong in choe3 hoan7-lang5 ah kau3 Siong7-hai2 e5 chip8-tiong-iann5.
Ti7 hia ka7 in koainn ti7 lim5-si5 e5 kann-gak8, si3-pinn u7 thong-tian7 chhi3-chhi3 e5 thih-soann3-bang7 ui5 teh. Koh tak8 e5 mng5 u7 oe7-peng giah8 chheng3 tau3 to, koh toa3 te2-chheng3, chhiu2-liu5-toann5, ki-koan-chheng3, ji5-chhiann2 u7 sun5-lo5-peng, kun-kau2, kam3-si7-thah, tham3-chiau3-teng, keng2-le5 e5 siat-pi7 lai5 kam3-si7 in, chit8-pou7 li2 to chau2 be7-tit chhut-khi3. Sou2 chiah8 chin bai2, tak8-jit8 kio3 chhut-khi3 sim2-mng7. U7-si5 hou7 in the2-heng5, u7-si5 si7 eng7 sim-li2-tek phi7-lo5 e5 sim2-mng7-hoat lai5 sim2-mng7. Chin7 in sou2 e7 e5 hiong-beng2 chau-that, chan5-jim2 lai5 khoan2-thai7 in. Hit si5 u7 che7-che7 lang5 tong3 be7-tiau5, ki5-tiong u7 Eng-kok, Bi2-kok e5 seng-li2-lang5, in koe3-khi3 ti7 Tai7-liok8 choe3 seng-li2 a2-si7 keng-eng5 kang-chhiunn2, long2 si7 ho2-giah8-lang5 toa7 lau2-pan2, kau3 chit si5 in u7 lang5 tong3 be7-tiau5 hoat-kong5 khi2-siau2, ia7 u7 eng7 siu-bin7 e5 to chu7-sat, u7 e5 chiah8 ai3-khun3-ioh8 lai5 si2.
Hit si5 ti7 hit tiong-kan u7 2 e5 soan-kau3-su, chit8 e5 si7 Bi2-kok-lang5, chit8 e5 si7 Eng-kok-lang5, chi2-u7 chit 2 lang5 in u7 Chu2 e5 an-ui3, chiu7 u7 chin e5 peng5-an kap khoai3-lok8 ti7 in e5 sim-tiong. In 2 lang5 siong5-siong5 ui7-tioh8 hiah e5 ki5-u5 e5 tang5-phoann7 lai5 ki5-to2. Ki5-tiong chit8 e5 khah siau3-lian5 e5 soan-kau3-su chin u7 jim2-nai7 e5 khui3-lat8. Sui-bong2 i ka-ki7 e5 chiah8-mih8 chin bai2 koh chio2, iau2-ku2 i siong5-siong5 khek-liam2 hou7 pat8-lang5, ka-ki7 lai5 jim2 iau-go7. U7-si5 khoann3 tioh8 tang5 siu7 koainn e5 lang5 phoa3-pinn7, i chiu7 khek-liam2 i e5 sou2-hui3 pa-kiat khan3-siu2 peng, peng ia7 kha3-iu5, chiu7 tui3 goa7-bin7 be2 tam7-poh8 mih8 jip8--lai5, i chiu7 chiong hiah e5 khah ho2 e5 mih8 lai5 sang3 phoa3-pinn7 e5 peng5-iu2 chiah8, choe3 chhin-chhiunn7 hou7-su7 lai5 hok8-sai7 hiah e5 u7 pinn7 e5 tang5-phoann7. Ia7 bat tu2-tioh8 loh8-seh e5 mi5, in e5 kann-pang5 bo5 hoe2-lou5 e5 siat-pi7, hiah e5 khah ni5-lau7 hiat-khi3 khah kou-soe e5 lang5 chin koann5, i chiu7 chiong phoe7 niu7 in kah, ka-ki7 koann5 kui-mi5 bo5 khun3, lai5 ho2 khoan2-thai7 pat8-lang5.
Bian2-loa7-ku2 thong-iann5 e5 lang5 long2 chin kam2-kek i e5 heng5-ui5. Tai7-ke chai i si7 soan-kau3-su, iau2-ku2 i ui7-tioh8 sou2 hok8-sai7 e5 Chu2, u7 chiong Ia5-sou e5 sim choe3 sim i chiu7 kam-goan7 hi-seng ka-ki7 lai5 hok8-sai7 pat8-lang5. Chhin-chhiunn7 choe3 lang5 e5 lou5-pok8, chong2-si7 tui3 i e5 sou2 choe3 si7 hou7 Chu2 e5 mia5 tit-tioh8 eng5-kng. Chin-chiann3 si7 chit8-khoan2 bu5-gian5 e5 thoan5-to7. Tai7-ke chin chun-keng3 i. Thang kong2 i si7 choe3 choan5-iann5 te7-it ui2-tai7 e5 jin5-but8, te7-it hou7 lang5 chun-keng3 khoann3-tang7 e5 lang5.
Siann2-su7 i e5 pinn3-choe3 an2-ni? M7-si7 i u7 sim2-mih8 se3-lek8, koan5-peng2. Si7 chai7 ti7 i u7 sit8-heng5 Chu2 e5 ka3-si7, kam-goan7 khiam-pi cho3 lang5 e5 chhe-eng7 lai5 hok8-sai7 pat8-lang5. Tui3 an2-ni i ka-ki7 e5 sim-lai7 oe7 senn-chhut bo5-han7 e5 hoann-hi2 kap khoai3-lok8.
